icipal da Avenids de Lagos ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0085_mercado_municipal_da_avenids_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0085_mercado_municipal_da_avenids_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.10422,"longitude":-8.673062},"summary":"Mercado Municipal da Avenida de Lagos is a colourful market famous for its fresh, locally-caught fish. ","url":"/poi/algarve/mercado-municipal-da-avenids-de-lagos","category":"Shopping Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0082","title":"Monte da Casteleja Winery ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0082_monte_da_casteleja_winery_0515_rfis_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0082_monte_da_casteleja_winery_0515_rfis_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.13057,"longitude":-8.684741},"summary":"Monte da Casteleja winery is a 10-minute drive from Lagos. ","url":"/poi/algarve/monte-da-casteleja-winery","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0092","title":"Museu Municipal","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0092_museu_municipal_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0092_museu_municipal_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.09941,"longitude":-8.671184},"summary":"Museu Municipal, Lagos' town museum, has a collection of archaeological finds from the area. ","url":"/poi/algarve/museu-municipal","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0093","title":"Ponta da Piedade","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0093_ponta_da_piedade_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0093_ponta_da_piedade_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.08064,"longitude":-8.669266},"summary":"These beautiful coastal cliffs have been weathered over the centuries into rock pillars, caves, grottoes and sea arches. ","url":"/poi/algarve/ponta-da-piedade","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0094","title":"Ponta da Piedade Lighthouse","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0094_ponta_da_piedade_lighthouse_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0094_ponta_da_piedade_lighthouse_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.08055,"longitude":-8.669549},"summary":"The lighthouse is Ponta da Piedade is a great spot to enjoy the views of the coast. ","url":"/poi/algarve/ponta-da-piedade-lighthouse","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0071","title":"Praia de Porto de Mos","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0071_praia_de_porto_de_mos_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0071_praia_de_porto_de_mos_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.08544,"longitude":-8.688133},"summary":"The golden sands of Porto de Mos are far less crowded than Meia Praia beach and if you head there out of season you could have the entire cove to yourself. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-de-porto-de-mos","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0072","title":"Praia do Canavial ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0072_praia_do_canavial_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0072_praia_do_canavial_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.08399,"longitude":-8.679311},"summary":"Praia do Canavial is a hidden gem but to get to it you need to tackle some steep, unsteady steps. ","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-do-canavial","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0073","title":"Praia Dona Ana","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0073_praia_dona_ana_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0073_praia_dona_ana_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.09164,"longitude":-8.66924},"summary":"","url":"/poi/algarve/praia-dona-ana","category":"Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0083","title":"Pro Putting Garden Lagos","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/lagos/fao0083_pro_putting _garden_lagos_184143125_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/lagos/fao0083_pro_putting _garden_lagos_184143125_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.09769,"longitude":-8.673828},"summary":"Pro Putting Garden has two mini golf courses, a nine-hole children’s course and a full 18-hole course for adults. ","url":"/poi/algarve/pro-putting-garden-lagos","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0077","title":"Restaurante o Camilo","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0077_restaurante_o_camilo_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0077_restaurante_o_camilo_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.0869,"longitude":-8.669637},"summary":"Overlooking Praia do Camilo is Restaurante o Camilo, which is famous for its menu and amazing views of the ocean. ","url":"/poi/algarve/restaurante-o-camilo","category":"Eating And Drinking Beaches"},{"code":"FAO0095","title":"Santa Maria Church","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0095_santa_maria_church_0316_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/algarve/fao0095_santa_maria_church_0316_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Lagos, Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.10017,"longitude":-8.670671},"summary":"This church overlooks a square centred on a statue of Henry the Navigator. ","url":"/poi/algarve/santa-maria-church","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0244","title":"Ria Formosa","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0244_ria_formosa_530009166_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0244_ria_formosa_530009166_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01831,"longitude":-8.003279},"summary":"What better way to spend a winter break on the Algarve than with a spot of birdwatching? ","url":"/poi/algarve/ria-formosa","category":"Activities"},{"code":"","title":"Capela dos Ossos","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5005_capela_dos_ossos_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5005_capela_dos_ossos_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":38.56895,"longitude":-7.90827},"summary":"The Capela dos Ossos was built by a Franciscan monk in the 16th century and lined with the exhumed skeletons of hundreds of his peers as a meditation on mortality and eternity. ","url":"/poi/algarve/capela-dos-ossos","category":"Sights"},{"code":"","title":"Cathedral of Faro","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5006_cathedral_of_faro_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5006_cathedral_of_faro_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01331,"longitude":-7.934949},"summary":"Like many of Faro’s churches, its Cathedral was built on the site of a Moorish mosque. ","url":"/poi/algarve/cathedral-of-faro","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0246","title":"Christmas in Vila Real de Santo Antonio ","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0246_vila_real_de_santo antonio_499539421_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0246_vila_real_de_santo antonio_499539421_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.19455,"longitude":-7.420902},"summary":"Want to experience the Algarve at its most authentic? ","url":"/poi/algarve/christmas-in-vila-real-de-santo-antonio","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0063","title":"Day trip to Lisbon","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0063_day_trip_lisbon_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0063_day_trip_lisbon_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.01792,"longitude":-7.930755},"summary":"Europe’s second oldest city is perfect if you want the best of both worlds – city break and beach holiday. ","url":"/poi/algarve/day-trip-to-lisbon","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0064","title":"Day trip to Seville","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0064_day_trip_seville_532854259_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0064_day_trip_seville_532854259_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.10746,"longitude":-8.676301},"summary":"Stroll down the cobbled streets of the Santa Cruz quarter, making your way to the Alcazar Palace drinking in the scent of orange blossom, or climb the steps in the Giralda tower for the view across the city. ","url":"/poi/algarve/day-trip-to-seville","category":"Activities"},{"code":"","title":"Ilha da Culatra","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":36.98891,"longitude":-7.833611},"summary":"Grab your beach parasol and head to Ilha da Culatra for the day. ","url":"/poi/algarve/ilha-da-culatra","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0243","title":"Loulé Carnival","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1389,"longitude":-8.022492},"summary":"If you want to explore a lesser-known side of the Algarve, Loul&eacute; is a great place to start. ","url":"/poi/algarve/loule-carnival","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0144","title":"Mercado de Loulé","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/